Text: Don't be fooled by the positive comments, this copy is an exact copy of the upload by user "TheCloon", which has received a whole lot of negative comments on the terrible audio quality, and rightfully so. Once you get about 8 minutes into the video the sound begins to play up and its REALLY annoying, trust me.
Can someone upload "The Lost Prince" about Prince John "Johnny", the younger brother of George VI'. Preferably in HD? If you like 'The Kings Speech' you'll enjoy 'The lost Prince'.
